<!-- ====================================================
     SECTION 1: PROCESS TIMELINE
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="process-section" id="process" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">注册全流程</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="process-heading">从零到公司成立<br>七步清晰指引</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">每个步骤配备时间预估与所需文件清单，首次注册者也能独立完成。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">1</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Day 1</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">确定公司名称 · 查册核名</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">在香港公司注册处（CR）搜索拟用公司名，确保无重复及不涉及受限词语。中文名需附英文名，不可单独注册纯中文名。查册可在 e-Registry 系统实时完成，通常 1–2 小时出结果。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">2</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Day 1–2</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">准备公司章程 · 确定股东董事架构</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">《公司章程》（Articles of Association）定义公司运营框架。至少需要 1 名股东（自然人或法人）、1 名董事（须为自然人）及 1 名本地公司秘书。董事与股东可为同一人。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">3</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Day 2–3</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">提交注册申请 · 缴纳政府费用</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">通过 e-Registry 在线提交「成立申请表格」（NNC1 或 NNC1G）、章程细则及注册费。政府注册费为 HK$1,720（同时申请商业登记证附加 HK$1,000）。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">4</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Day 5–8</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">获取公司注册证书 · 商业登记证</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">获批后领取「成立法团证书」（Certificate of Incorporation）及一年期「商业登记证」（Business Registration Certificate）。电子申请约 3–4 个工作日，纸本约 7–10 日。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">5</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Day 8–10</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">制作公司钢印 · 签署股份证书</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">刻制公司圆形钢印（Common Seal）用于正式文件签署。向股东签发股份证书（Share Certificate），首次股东会议通过相关决议。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">6</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">Week 2–3</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">银行开户 · 激活业务账户</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">凭注册文件向汇丰、渣打、中银等传统银行或 Airwallex、Statrys 等数字银行申请企业账户。传统银行需本人到场面签，数字银行可全程线上完成，3–5 工作日批核。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"><span class="timeline-dot-num">7</span></div>
        <div class="timeline-body">
          <span class="timeline-tag">持续</span>
          <div class="timeline-title">年审合规 · 维持良好法团状态</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">每年按时续期商业登记证（HK$2,200/年）、提交周年申报表（Annual Return）及必要时申报税务。保持良好合规记录有助维持银行关系与公司信用。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


